# Async Frontier MMO — project context

**Not a Godot project.** The client is a web/PWA built with SvelteKit. Godot is out of scope unless Ryan explicitly asks.

## North star

Menu/text-first async frontier MMO: Farm RPG growth path + Firefall thumper fantasy + SWG-style named resources and crafting.

## Core toy (build this first)

```text
Survey → thump → craft → equip/use → decay → survey better
```

Stay in **pre-production** until a tiny vertical slice proves the loop is fun. Do not add chat, marketplace, realtime, planets, or combat boards until the personal thumper loop works.

